OL,3,CUnions look to improved employment
OL,4,Crelations under a Labour government
OL,6,FUnion leaders have accused the
OL,7,FConservative Government of misjudging
OL,8,Fthe public mood over strikes following
OL,9,Fan unprecedented wave of industrial
OL,10,Faction stretching back two years.
OL,12,FThey expressed hopes that an incoming
OL,13,FLabour government will improve
OL,14,Femployment relations amid ongoing
OL,15,Fwalkouts by workers.
