OL,3,CUnions look to improved employment
OL,4,Crelations under a Labour government
OL,6,FDisputes remain unresolved, including
OL,7,Fthose involving train drivers,
OL,8,Fseafarers, jobcentre security guards,
OL,9,Fand junior doctors, who will be on
OL,10,Fstrike again in England for five days
OL,11,Ffrom June 27.
OL,13,FUnion leaders blame the Conservative
OL,14,FGovernment for many of the disputes,
OL,15,Fespecially in the public sector, where
OL,16,Fpay has failed to keep pace with
OL,17,Finflation for more than a decade.
