OL,3,CUnions look to improved employment
OL,4,Crelations under a Labour government
OL,6,FPaul Nowak, general secretary of the
OL,7,FTUC, believes the Government
OL,8,Fcompletely misjudged the mood of
OL,9,Fworkers and the public.
OL,11,F"Ministers thought they could turn the
OL,12,Fpublic against workers going on
OL,13,Fstrike, but the complete opposite
OL,14,Fhappened," he told the PA news agency.
OL,16,F"The Government's response to the
OL,17,Findustrial action was to bring in
OL,18,Fdraconian legislation on minimum
OL,19,Fservice levels during strikes, which
OL,20,Fno employer has been reckless enough
OL,21,Fto use.
