OL,4,Crelations under a Labour government
OL,6,FMick Lynch, general secretary of the
OL,7,FRail, Maritime and Transport (RMT)
OL,8,Funion, accused the Government of being
OL,9,Fbehind the many disputes in the
OL,10,Frailway industry.
OL,12,FHe told PA: "They could have settled
OL,13,Fdisputes more quickly if they had
OL,14,Fallowed unions to get on with the job
OL,15,Fof engaging in industrial relations."
OL,17,FMr Lynch said public sector workers
OL,18,Fwill be looking for quick settlements
OL,19,Funder a Labour government which will
OL,20,F"calm things down".
