OL,3,CUnions look to improved employment
OL,4,Crelations under a Labour government
OL,6,F"The economic chaos of the Tory
OL,7,FGovernment has been the background to
OL,8,Fthe disputes because it has had a huge
OL,9,Fimpact on workplaces across the
OL,10,Fcountry," he told PA.
OL,12,F"There has also been a new era of
OL,13,Ftrade union leaders and activists.
OL,15,F"Labour's New Deal will be a very
OL,16,Fpowerful signal of the desire to
OL,17,Finvolve working people and give them a
OL,18,Fvoice after the Government and
OL,19,Femployers have been refusing to listen
OL,20,Fto legitimate concerns.
