OL,6,FUniversity and College Union general
OL,7,Fsecretary Jo Grady said: "Two years on
OL,8,Ffrom the summer of discontent, workers
OL,9,Facross the country have made big
OL,10,Fgains, and our members have helped
OL,11,Flead the way.
OL,13,F"The University and College Union
OL,14,Fmobilised like never before, winning
OL,15,Fnot one but two national ballots, and
OL,16,Fforcing universities to agree to
OL,17,Frestore our retirement benefits in
OL,18,Ffull. This is the biggest pensions win
OL,19,Fin British trade union history.
