OL,6,F"Meanwhile, in further education, we
OL,7,Ftook strike action for fair pay across
OL,8,FEngland, winning pay awards of up to
OL,9,F12% at over 60 colleges.
OL,11,F"We now need to keep up the fight and
OL,12,Fmake sure workers everywhere get their
OL,13,Ffair share."
OL,15,FKevin Hollinrake, small business
OL,16,Fminister, said: "The Labour manifesto
OL,17,Fmakes clear that a Labour government
OL,18,Fwould hand over power to the unions,
OL,19,Fleading to a massive increase in taxes
OL,20,Fto accommodate outlandish trade union
